    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"ariadne-entry\"><p><strong>Source:</strong> Ariadne's Book of Legends - Alpha v1.2, p. 91.</p><p>Tier III: Hierophant</p><p>Prerequisite: Exalted Presence, Hierophant’s Sanctuary, Perfected Boons, Chooser of Conduits</p><p>Great Guide. Your Amplified Boons and Amplified Magic features now allow you to target three times the number of creatures a spell or feature normally allows. The range of your Hierophant’s Sanctuary aura expands to 60 feet.</p><p>Word of Creation. As an action, you speak a word of creation, replicating the effects of any spell of 9th level or lower that you are familiar with. Once you use this ability, you cannot do so again until you finish a long rest.</p><p>Path Connections Herald. Instead of the Hierophant’s Sanctuary Heroic Perk, you can take the Divine Arrival Perk, changing to the Herald path.</p><p>Sovereign. Instead of the Hierophant’s Sanctuary Heroic Perk, you can take the Greater Charms Perk, changing to the Sovereign path.</p><p>Third Eye. Instead of the Chooser of Conduits Heroic Perk, you can take the Ascended Mind Perk, changing to the Third Eye path.</p></div>",
